OOC: Sorry about the other one... dumbass AOL

::Aerotaur::
       He sees Flicker flipping over him and before Flicker lands he executes 
a quick backflip over Flicker.  He lands behind him and raises his arm a 
small blaster popping out of the back of it.  "Don't I though?"

       Unfortunately this flip put him directly in the line of fire from 
Owlhawk.  The series of blasts catch him square in the back and he winces 
lowering his arm.  He finally collapses to his knees and falls forward onto 
Nightlight and, possibly, Flicker's legs.

--part1_1ac.12a3626b.2bbb4a0c_boundary
